---
title: Creamy Mussel Chowder with Toasted Ciabatta
description: It's CHOWDA time! Enjoy creamy dreamy mussels in a velvety cream sauce with diced yellow potatoes, peas and celery. A  crispy ciabatta to dip is the perfect pairing for this powerhouse meal!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creamy-mussel-chowder-9de1a5de.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.ca/recipecards/card/creamy-mussel-chowder-5db0d7adbd7f5d4f2c2090dc-73079ebe.pdf
